      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANDIT DARYL (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 43.03 beating Statue Of Time. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Flying at the moment and expecting another big run. ADHANA MADI (1) missed the frame latest when fifth at this track (43.73) but was a winner four back in the best time of the program. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Can figure in the finish. OREGON JANET (4) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (40.01) at Murray Bridge. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature. ZIPPING MOWGLI (6) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when second (34.90) in a Special conditions race over 595m at this track.",
